hey have all the answers you could easily develop a distrust of the entire industry a quick bit of research on pubmed or even just wikipedia or webmd will lead you to information about how some herbs really do help with sex drive and erection strength so there must be some legitimate supplements out there the struggle is in finding a company has the right combinations of highlyconcentrated herbs backed by research and science and that other men use again and again because it works it’s no wonder i’ve gotten so many emails asking what male enhancement pills i recommend some of you are so sick of the malarkey that you’re ready to resort to the “blue pill” i’m happy to tell you that you don’t have to you don’t need to suffer from extreme headaches just to get an erection and satisfy your partner i’m answering your calls for help today there are effective male enhancement supplements out there and i’m going to help you find them you can spend your money on something that is a legitimate investment in yourself and your health best of all you can attain the sexual satisfaction you deserve the science of erections you probably already know this by now but i’m going to rehash it just in case there are chambers in the penis that fill up with blood to make it erect the full process is a little bit more complicated than that but that’s the important part so to find an effective supplement you need to find something that helps the blood fill the chambers and keeps them filled there are several factors that can complicate this process some of the factors are mental depression stress anxiety some are physical circulation hormones diabetes a good supplement will address these factors and counteract any effect they might be having on your sex drive how to spot a scam these are my top  red flags i use to avoid throwing money away  prescription strength this might be obvious but be mindful of any herbal supplement that exaggerates its effectiveness if a company is trying to tell you that their supplement can run sidebyside with a prescription drug immediately look to its ingredients and user reviews and let common sense be your guide  free trial when a company offers to give you a free product and asks you to just pay for shipping they enter you into a subscription as soon as you give them your credit card info the subscription becomes nearly impossible to cancel so whether the product works or not you’re stuck paying for it again and again  the product promises to add inches to your member as i mentioned before every penis has chambers that fill up with blood during an erection those chambers determine the size of an erect penis aside from surgery there is no way to change the size of those chambers there is no magic pill that permanently adds inches and girth some supplements will claim to “maximize size” that’s different——that just means they promise their pill will help fully fill the existing chambers  if the website looks amateur this one is probably obvious if the site has simple coding errors where buttons don’t line up or if there are obvious misspellings all over be warned if a company can’t afford to hire a decent web designer how can they afford to develop an effective supplement  if it’s not made in america foreignmade products are not subject to fda scrutiny and might be full of ingredients that are completely worthless or are rendered worthless by sitting in shipping crates on container ships for months at a time some of these supplements may do more harm than good how to spot a lifechanger there are multiple ways to identify a good product i reveal my full process in identifying good products later in this article for now here’s a general rule rather than look at the ingredients in the product look at the research behind the ingredients don’t trust a company that doesn’t do its homework or that won’t show it to you a credible company will share their research with you you know they’re confident in their product if they demonstrate that they have nothing to hide they will be able to show you exactly how the ingredients in their product will get you these results harder longerlasting erections improved sex drive maximized size boosted mood  confidence satisfied partners more intimate love life sexual satisfaction how we rated our winners now that i have helped you avoid the time and money wasters it’s time to fill you in on how my search for effective supplements went the male enhancement market is huge my research team and i sorted through hundreds of the supplements out there i’m ready to help you find the good ones at supplement review digest we’ve shopped around and seen it all so that you don’t have to we’ve selected the top  male enhancement supplements that i believe are actually worth your money these brands were selected based on the research safety and effectiveness of their chosen ingredients consistently high customer reviews and how well they performed in our inhouse doubleblind trials against placebos my team had two groups take pills for  months one group took a product the other a placebo and report back to us weekly with their results our male enhancement groups had individuals who reported improvements in ability to get and maintain erections the placebo groups reported no gains we ranked the products by which group had the highest number of erectionachieving men at the end of the trial period and by these  factors  customer reviews  purity of ingredients  are fda guidelines followed  research  scientific evidence  speed of expected result  customer service  types of ingredients in formula  price  return policy our top picks  rated asox created by harvard biology graduate it is our top pick  rated high t black newest product form king fisher  rated steel libido red irvin naturals revamped red formula what you will learn ✔ how to select the best product ✔ what common scams to watch out for ✔ which supplements are backed by studies ✔ top tested products rating factors custome